N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12 ยง 601.17 - Severability

State Regulations

If any provision of this Part or the application to any
person or circumstance is held invalid, the remainder of this Part and the
application of such provision to other persons or circumstances shall not be
affected thereby. Notes
